actionConfiguration.body:
INSERT INTO WeighBridge (
	Docket,
	WB_Docket,
	Date,
	Rego,
	Supplier,
	Operations,
	Coupe,
	Harvestor,
	FPP,
	Gross,
	Tare,
	GMT,
	Grade,
	Length
)
VALUES (
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.DocketIn}}',
	'{{iw_data_table.selectedRow.WB_Docket}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.DateIn.split('T')[0]}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.RegoIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.SupplierIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.OperationsIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.CoupeIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.HarvestorIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.FPPIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.GrossIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.TareIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.GMTIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.GradeIn}}',
	'{{Edit_Invalid.data.LengthIn}}'
);
DELETE FROM Invalid_WeighBridge
  WHERE WB_Docket = {{iw_data_table.selectedRow.WB_Docket}};
